<h1 style="color:white;background-color:red;">Hades, a breakthrough in gaming.</h1>
<img src="https://assets.nintendo.com/image/upload/c_fill,w_1200/q_auto:best/f_auto/dpr_2.0/ncom/en_US/games/switch/h/hades-switch/hero" width="600" height="337.5" alt="Hades title card">
<p>Hades is a roguelike indie video game, developed my Supergiant Games. </p>
<p>Supergiant Games, is a San Fransisco  based video game development company. It was founded in 2009 by Amir Rao and Gavin Simon. While they have been in the video game industry for years, with titles such as Bastion (insert link), Transistor, and Pyre, the success of their 2020 release Hades has surpassed the popularity of all their former games. </p>
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/54/Supergiant_games_logo.png/220px-Supergiant_games_logo.png" width-"416" height="240" alt="Supergiant games logo">
